{
  "id": "adv_main_03_10_03",
  "title": "BIG4編1章48話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_dangerous-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_office_evening",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_03-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "それでは……まず私からいかせてもらいますね\n琴乃ちゃん。あなたは……自分勝手が過ぎます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well then… I'll go first.\nKotono. You… are way too selfish.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_03-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "月ストのセンターとしての責任を果たそうと\nストイックに考えていた、と言えば聞こえはいいですが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You might make it sound nice by saying you were being stoic\nand trying to fulfill your responsibilities as Moon Tempest's center‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.4881706238,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_03-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "その過程を私達と共有せず、一方的に脱退したいと\n言われた時、私達がどれだけショックだったか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "but when you told us you wanted to quit without discussing it with us‚\ndo you have any idea how shocked we were…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_03-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "それに、私達には沢山の支えてくれる人達がいるんです\nそんな人達とも連絡を絶つなんてもってのほかです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Besides‚ we have a lot of people supporting us.\nIt’s unacceptable for you to just cut off contact with them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_03-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "「まだ高校生だし」では済まされませんよ\nプロのアイドルだという自覚が欠けています",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You can't just brush this off by saying \"I'm still in high school.\"\nYou lack the awareness of being a professional idol.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_03-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "……うん。全部沙季の言う通り\nどれだけ謝っても許されることじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "……Yeah. Everything you're saying is right‚ Saki.\nNo amount of apologies can make up for this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_03-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "……と、まぁ、散々な言い方をしましたけど\n琴乃ちゃんから私達に言いたいことだってあるでしょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Well‚ I might've been a bit harsh‚\nbut I'm sure Kotono-chan has things she wants to say to us too‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_main-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 58
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_03-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "だから、一層本音で話し合っていきましょう\nまたグループを組むなら……それが条件です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So let's talk openly and honestly.\nIf we're going to be a group again… that's my condition.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_03-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "……ありがとう、言ってくれて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Thank you for telling me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.6741017979,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_03-ski008.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃあ次は……すずちゃん\n琴乃ちゃんへの気持ちを伝えてもらえますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay then‚ next is… Suzu-chan.\nCould you tell Kotono-chan how you feel?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_sad-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 88.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_03-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ……琴乃。あなたって、私が思っていたより……\nずっっっっっと、大バカですわね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes… Kotono. You… are much…\nmuch more of an idiot than I thought!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_03-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "あなたがいなくなった日。私達は泣きましたわ\n揃いも揃って大泣きしましたのよ！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The day you disappeared. We cried.\nWe all cried our eyes out!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_03-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "その後もあなたは心配ばかりかけて……\n私達の気持ちを少しでも想像したことがあります！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And even after that‚ you only caused us worry…\nHave you ever even tried to imagine how we felt!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.5333318074,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_03-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "……ごめん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I'm sorry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.4459868749,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_03-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "謝って済む話じゃありませんわ。絶対に許しません！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This isn't something you can just apologize for. I'll never forgive you!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.0519460042,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_03-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "あなたが月ストのセンターとしてどれほど大変だったか\n……私はセンターになって、初めて気付きました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How hard it was for you to be Moon Tempest's center…\n…I only realized after becoming the center myself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.5999984741,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_03-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "あなたの悩みを想像して、苦しくて、辛くて……\nでも、あなたはもういなくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I imagined your struggles‚ and it was painful and agonizing…\nBut you were already gone…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.5999984741,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_03-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "気持ちをぶつけられないことがどれだけ辛かったか……\n……この仕打ちは、一生忘れませんわよ……っ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How painful it was not being able to tell you how I felt…\n…I'll never forget this… ever… sob!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.7999984741,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_03-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "うん……すず、ごめんね。ありがとう……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah… I'm sorry‚ Suzu. Thank you…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.5945076944,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tension-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 155.7333318074
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_03-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "なんでお礼を言われなきゃならないんですの……！？\nうわぁぁ～ん……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why are you thanking me……!?\nWaaaaah……!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.7333318074,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_03-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "……ぐすっ、うぅぅ～\n琴乃！　いいですこと！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Sniff‚ uuuu～\nKotono! You better not disappoint me!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_03-suz010.m4a",
      "text": "今度スタジオで、琴乃が積み上げてきたものを\n見せてくださいまし！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Next time at the studio‚ you better show me\nwhat you've been working on!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 169.0733828891,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_03-suz011.m4a",
      "text": "歌でも、ダンスでも！　生半可なものを見せたりしたら\nあなたとグループなんて組みませんわよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whether it's singing or dancing! If you show me anything half-assed‚\nI won't be in a group with you!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 175.8666651408,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_03-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "……うん、分かったわ、すず",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Okay‚ I understand‚ Suzu.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 178.7833329362,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_03-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃ……次は私かな？\n……ねぇ、琴乃ちゃん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So… am I next?\n…Hey‚ Kotono-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 190.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_03-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "私ね、琴乃ちゃんのことずーっと心配してた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was really worried about you‚ Kotono-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 193.2638544005,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_03-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "心配してたのは私達だけじゃないんだよ\nでもさ、沙季ちゃんも言ってたけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And it wasn't just us who were worried.\nBut like Saki-chan said…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 198.0215868396,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_03-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "四人の活動を応援してくれる人もいたけど、やっぱり\n「五人じゃないと寂しい」って人も沢山いたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There were people who supported us as a four-member group‚ but…\n…there were a lot of people who said \"It's lonely without all five of you\".",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 212,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_trouble-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 221.0999877929
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
